reviews.product_title: Novartis Capstar Flea Tablets for Dogs and Cats
reviews.review_body: My cat had the worst flea infestation she had ever had. Because is 15 years old i feared giving her a treatment to toxic and thus harmful.  Capstar worked within ONE HOUR! I worried about how to give  her a pill. No problem, crushed the pill and mixed with wet food. Again, it worked like noting else and NO side effects. Now one pill a week does the trick.

reviews.product_title: PetSafe Simply Clean Self-Cleaning Cat Litter Box, Automatic, Works with Clumping Cat Litter
reviews.review_body: This box never worked for me.  I followed the directions to the letter.  First of all, the sides are not tall enough.  My cats got litter every where.  I literally burned up a vacuum trying to get all of the litter up off of the carpet.  Second of all, it never scooped up any of the clumped litter into the little bin.  Third of all, it takes the regular shopping bags that you put into the bin, and they get wrapped around the metal part that turns the conveyor belt, burning out the motor.    I would NOT recommend this box to anyone.  If you want an automatic box, go with something different.  I should have known it was junk when the person at the pet store told me \\"make sure you keep your receipt.\\"

reviews.product_title: Stink Bug Trap By Sterling International Rescue
reviews.review_body: I have had one of these up for about two weeks and caught -one- stinkbug. And this was -after- it was placed in an area with a visible, heavy concentration of them. It sits right now with dozens of them within several feet of it. None of them find it the least bit interesting, there is no increased concentration of them near it. Useless waste of money.

reviews.product_title: EnergyFlux Ellipse Rechargeable Hand Warmer 5200mAh / USB Portable Charger Power Bank Battery Pack
reviews.review_body: I purchased this because I'm attending school in MN and it was going to be extremely cold - and it was! It did help me cope with the subzero temperatures and I'm grateful. However, I also looked forward to using it as a battery pack and I was rather disappointed. I was never able to get it to charge my phone. All the cords were connected and it seemed fine but my phone never got charged. Not even for a second. Also, even when I think I've charged it fully, the light on my device continues to flash orange. Perhaps I got a faulty one. Still, it's useful as a hand warmer - I just wish I got to use it as a battery pack as well.

reviews.product_title: HP PSC 1315 All-in-One Printer
reviews.review_headline: PC Load Letter?  What the *$%& does that mean?
reviews.review_body: I hate this printer.  I got it super cheap when a local Circuit City closed down and sold off floor models.  I design business cards, pamplets, etc. on my computer as a side business while going to college and suffice to say, printing them on this printer can't happen.  Nothing lines up correctly.  It completly ignores the margins I've set.  Everything prints at a slanted angle.  And then to make it even better, it will print say 3 pages perfect and then never print it right again. I have to say that this printer works great for printing non-coloured documents, but DO NOT BUY THIS PRINTER if you need it to print on anything other than standard paper.  It will not do it.

reviews.product_title: Mohu Leaf 30 TV Antenna, Indoor, 30 Mile Range, Original Paper-thin, Reversible, Paintable, 4K-Ready HDTV, 10 Foot Detachable Cable, Premium Materials for Performance, USA Made, MH-110583
reviews.review_headline: Easy to install and excellent reception
reviews.review_body: When I moved into my new apartment, the reception was so poor that I was only able to get a couple of channels. The channels I did receive came in and out. The Leaf Indoor Antenna perfectly fixed the problem and we now get over 40 channels. I followed the recommendation to tape up the antenna and check to see which channels it received. Moving it around (I actually moved it further down the wall) allowed me to find a place where I received all the channels I wanted before affixing to the wall. The install could not have been more simple and easy. Now, we get a lot of channels without loss of signal. I am very happy with this product. Looking at the other reviews, I think I should mention that I live in New York City, much more urban than other reviewers who were less satisfied.

reviews.product_title: Super Mesh Magnetic Screen Door - Magic Mesh Instant Screen Door Insect & Fly Screens Set
reviews.review_body:
I live in the South. Leaving doors open without a screen in the hot Summer is a terrible mistake. Mosquitoes and flies will fly inside like crazy. However, I really enjoy opening the door sometimes and letting fresh air into the house. Especially after a good fresh rain shower. I got tired of mosquito bites, so I decided to order this Magic Mesh Magnetic Screen Door. The fact that it is covered in butterflies was just icing on the cake for me. I absolutely love butterflies.

The day my new Screen arrived, I had my hubby to hang it up. The screen is very simple to install. It comes with a package of velcro strips and a small box of tacs. I could have easily installed it myself if only I was taller. It only took my husband maybe 5 minutes or less to install. It looks gorgeous in my true opinion. I really love my new Screen. The butterflies just stand out so well. Several of my neighbors have complimented it just in the past few days.

This Screen is made of good quality materials. The materials used to hang it are made good also. For the great price that the Screen is available for, this deal just can't be beat. Your not gonna get a good quality screen like this from anywhere else. I have tried other mesh screens in the past. None of them were made as well as this one. I am very pleased with it.

* I received this Magic Mesh Magnetic Screen for free in exchange for my honest and unbiased review.
